// >>> SWAP-IN POINT FOR SUPERLINKED <<<
// To rank semantically instead, REPLACE this Code node with an HTTP Request node:
//   POST https://<your-superlinked-endpoint>/query
//   Body: { intent, area, property_type, beds, budget_max, must_haves }
//   Map its ranked results into an array called `matches` with the SAME shape
//   used below (id, title, type, area, price, beds, features). Keep the
//   request/response contract identical so the swap is free. (architecture.md stage 3)
//
// You can also replace the inline LISTINGS below with a live Attio query:
//   HTTP Request -> POST https://api.attio.com/v2/objects/listings/records/query
//   (Bearer <ATTIO_TOKEN>) and feed the returned records in here.

